{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"Tender Extract API","description":"Extract comprehensive information from South African government tender PDF documents including description, requirements, B-BBEE details, contact information, dates, and more. Uses regex-based pattern matching optimized for SA tender formats.","version":"1.0.0"},"paths":{"/health":{"get":{"tags":["System"],"summary":"Health Check","description":"Health check endpoint for deployment monitoring.","operationId":"health_check_health_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HealthResponse"}}}}}}},"/v1/extract":{"post":{"tags":["Extraction"],"summary":"Extract Tender","description":"Extract comprehensive tender information from a PDF.\n\nAccepts either:\n- A PDF file via multipart/form-data upload\n- A JSON body with a URL to fetch the PDF from\n\nReturns comprehensive extracted data including:\n- **Core**: description, requirements\n- **Identification**: tender_number, title\n- **Dates**: closing_date, closing_time, validity_period, contract_period\n- **Organization**: issuing_organization, department\n- **Financial**: estimated_value, bid_bond_required, payment_terms\n- **B-BBEE**: minimum_level, points_allocation, details\n- **Contact**: name, email, phone, department, address\n- **Sessions**: briefing_session details\n- **Additional**: evaluation_criteria, special_conditions, returnable_documents\n\nError Codes:\n- 415: Not a PDF file\n- 422: Validation error (file too large, invalid input)\n- 501: Scanned PDF (requires OCR, not supported)\n- 504: URL fetch timeout","operationId":"extract_tender_v1_extract_post","requestBody":{"content":{"multipart/form-data":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Body_extract_tender_v1_extract_post"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ExtractResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Valid